---
// Footer.astro - サイト全体のフッター
---

<footer class="relative bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-md border-t border-white/10 mt-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- ブランド情報 -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 to-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">T</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">Toriforiumu</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          ゲーム、開発、旅の軌跡を通じて，<br>
          多様な体験と技術を共有しています．
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- ナビゲーション -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">ナビゲーション</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
          <a href="#hero" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors duration-300 text-sm">Home</a>
          <a href="#about" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors duration-300 text-sm">About</a>
          <a href="#skills" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors duration-300 text-sm">Skills</a>
          <a href="#opus" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors duration-300 text-sm">Opus</a>
          <a href="#journey" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors duration-300 text-sm">Journey</a>
          <a href="#games" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors duration-300 text-sm">Games</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- ソーシャルリンク -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">Connect</h3>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <a href="https://github.com/torifo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 hover-lift group">
